Who We Are?

Raj Rani Foundation is a group of companions serving and working since 2017 mainly for tree plantation and blood donating camps. Now, we came with a mobile app 'Blood Friendz' to bring all the voluntary blood donors to a common platform. Blood donation will cost you nothing, but it will save a life.

  • Ability to present as a voluntary blood donor.
  • Ability to locate the nearest blood donor.
  • Ability to edit profile, change password , update last blood donation, delete profile and many other features.
  • Saved several lives so far.
